<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>스터띱 도서 게시글 수정페이지</title>

<link rel="stylesheet" href="./resources/assets/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet"
	href="./resources/assets/css/font-awesome.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet"
	href="./resources/assets/css/owl.carousel.min.css">
